Comment: 0,0:33:47.87,0:33:50.58,Note,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats went that way. ->
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:04.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desativou o castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estão vendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Somos o alvo de todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:20.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os insetos apareceram!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:25.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até aqui chegamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:02.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:04.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,M-Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:06.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que eu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero fazer parte disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:20.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:26.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Heavenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:30.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Reiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:46.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esqueçam dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:48.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Niji, Yonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É culpa dela por ser fraca!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cumpram sua missão!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que irmão cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:56.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como quiserem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vão me derrotar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:03.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou começar com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Garota da Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:10.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:13.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Crosse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:19.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas você disse para eu não sair! {english line: "You told me we weren't going all out!" different meaning of "going all out"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:29.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, você não deve sair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:30.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu posso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é justo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:33.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles saíram...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que vão fazer agora, idiotas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:17.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que estão tentando fugir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lembra do que você\N me disse, Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:29.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na Ilha dos Homens-Peixe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você disse que ia chutar minha bunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:40.72,Denden_recuerdo,,0,0,0,, Monkey D. Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.80,Denden_recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não vou te esquecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.97,Denden_recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Estarei te esperando no Novo Mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.77,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Claro, espere só!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.90,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou chutar sua bunda no Novo Mundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.57,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...e farei da Ilha dos Homens-Peixe \Nparte dos meus domínios!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:04.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lembra do que você\N me disse nesta ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:10.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você disse que seriam vocês\N quem venceriam no final.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.80,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,E você é quem não se tornou \No rei dos piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.34,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Isso é tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:18.84,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou te desafiar de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:22.68,Denden_recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não seja tão arrogante por ser uma Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.19,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou recuperar o Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:29.02,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Seremos nós quem\N venceremos no final!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E agora você foge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Covarde!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Co... co...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Covarde?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não caia em provocações, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só um golpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:48.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu disse tudo isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:15.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem será o Rei dos Piratas...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...serei eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:54.63,Title,,0,0,420,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Vamos, Caesar! {Spanish manga 871 title}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso, Germa! {pace 841, 11:25:48}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:57.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Continuem me protegendo assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desgraçados!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem enfrenta a mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:04.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...acaba queimado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Apareceu um forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse maldito Oven, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou começar com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuide do resto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Queimados?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:28.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Antes disso vou te dar uma surra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que insolente!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, só me leve para o outro lado do muro! {pace 841 14:91:94}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso que estou tentando fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ainda tem mais deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se superarmos esse muro, poderei escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lambida.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vão escapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Candy Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:07.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que diabos é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deve ser obra de Perospero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:13.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossa última esperança...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acabou...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:21.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Minha liberdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:22.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vai nos engolir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:23.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Dê meia-volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, continuem avançando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.02,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.98,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,...Bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.98,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2800,3300)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.98,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2800,3300)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.98,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2800,3300)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.98,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2800,3300)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.98,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2800,3300)}Inseto negro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(929,702)}Avançem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:48.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(248,702)}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(248,702)}Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles quebraram...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nos salvaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:06.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Germa 66!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles conseguiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Superaram a barreira de doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar da Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo sendo um lixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.67,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo sendo um lixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cheguei tão longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando eu superar o muro,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,serei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:31.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...livre!{\fad(0,350)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:39.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Caixa Tamate, o tesouro do fundo \Ndo mar, está à vista, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:45.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que teve que cair\N naquele lugar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:46.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que seja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou descer então...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você planeja fazer com\N a Caixa Tamate, Du Feld?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,V-Você é...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Stussy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você estava me observando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:06.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,D-Dói...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos agora poderei \Nver o que tem dentro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O tesouro do fundo do mar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:16.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver quanto vale!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tobu Shigan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:30.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A Caixa Tamate será levada\N por nós, o Governo Mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.65,OPLetreros,,50,0,40,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(665,450)\fad(398,500)}"RAINHA DA ZONA ROSA"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.65,OPLetreros,,50,0,40,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(675,690)\fad(398,500)}E TAMBÉM...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:35.62,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(399,0)\pos(339,435)}AGENTE DE INTELIGÊNCIA\NCP "AIGIS" 0
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:35.62,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(399,0)\pos(334,716)}STUSSY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:39.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro, você será o responsável.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você poderia escrever um\N artigo dizendo isso,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Morgans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.58,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ela me descobriu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:48.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, mas deixe-me ver \Npelo menos o interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, tire fotos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é muito sensato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar de um\N manipulador de informações.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, eu tenho um jornal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou te processar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,702)}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,702)}Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim que eu derrotar Kaidou,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,o próximo será você,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não é nada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:38.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você disse que era só um golpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kaidou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:48.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês não conseguirão\N derrotar aquela coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:54.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E vocês, desgraçados...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:12:01.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como é que sonham em\N escapar dos meus domínios?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:14.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nosso sonho foi arruinado...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:19.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há fantasmas que foram deixados para trás\N após sessenta e seis dias de sonho,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:23.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,e que não podem colocar\N um pé em seu país!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E agora não posso mais \Nolhar nos olhos deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E pensar que eu ia\N dar a alguém como você...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:47.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...meu país com trezentos anos de história\N e seu espírito de mortificação!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu me odeio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:57.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me afeta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Morra em paz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:05.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou usar sua tecnologia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:11.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...para alcançar a paz mundial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Raitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.00,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.00,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.00,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.00,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.00,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Trovão.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:42.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela o matou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.69,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, esperem, escoltas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão nos abandonar...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Katakuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estiveram perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quase conseguiram.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sparking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:18.75,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,3880,4380)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.37,0:14:18.75,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,3880,4380)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.37,0:14:18.75,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3880,4380)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.37,0:14:18.75,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3880,4380)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:14.37,0:14:18.75,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,3880,4380)}Figura cintilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Calma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos cumprir nossa missão!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Siga avançando!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não precisa me dizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acha que me pegou de surpresa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:36.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que você não valoriza sua vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:39.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não adianta tentar me intimidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu não sinto medo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não deixem eles escaparem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fogo, fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, vamos-rero! {8:19:56}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso, para frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que você seja escória!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:58.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você disse...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuidado, maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:05.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, saia daí!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.95,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Ei, saia daí!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.92,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.32,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.27,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Eu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:20.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, não pode ser eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:20.53,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Não, não pode ser eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:24.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sou eu, Caesar Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:25.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não vai escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:34.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tenho muito ressentimento\N contra vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Finalmente acertei algumas contas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:45.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bom, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Derrotaram todos eles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É aqui que chegamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:24.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:29.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nesse ritmo, todos vamos morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:41.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só resta uma opção.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Em vez de esperar pela morte...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É melhor lutar, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também vou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós também, é claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não tem jeito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Caixa Tamate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:30.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, que comecem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...as execuções.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.11,Principio,,0,0,0,,Voltando um pouco no tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.66,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(451,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}ILHA DOS HOMENS-PEIXE - REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:34.45,Principio,,0,0,0,,Luffy e os outros salvaram o Reino \NRyugu dos Novos Piratas Homens-Peixe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:39.48,Principio,,0,0,0,,...e o Rei Neptune lhes deu a\N Caixa Tamate como agradecimento.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.50,Principio,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.18,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sua Majestade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:48.36,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}É sobre o tesouro roubado que você entregará à \Ntripulação de Luffy-kun caso o encontrem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:52.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}Se possível, peça-lhes por favor\N a devolução da Caixa Tamate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.66,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O que você está dizendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:58.52,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não posso voltar atrás\N nas minhas palavras!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:02.27,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que, em vez de conter \Ntesouros,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:04.40,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,houvesse uma bomba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.65,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.53,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Haverá uma grande\N explosão se abrirem a caixa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:10.87,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Preciso pedir que a devolvam imediatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:17.83,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você entregou todo o tesouro à Big Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:17.83,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Você entregou todo o tesouro à Big Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:21.38,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Existe a possibilidade de que não \Nexploda, Ministro da Direita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:25.12,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sim, Majestade, temos que ser positivos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:30.02,OPLetreros,,0,970,365,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(750,0)\pos(160,395)}WHOLE CAKE ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:30.02,Principio,,0,0,0,,De volta ao presente...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:38.06,OPLetreros,,0,950,345,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(750,750)\pos(170,420)}DENTRO DO WHOLE CAKE CHÂTEAU {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma grande rachadura se estende\N desde o segundo andar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:38.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...do Pastel Baum Leste até a sala de\N reuniões do Pastel Baum de Feijões Vermelhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.25,Denden,,0,0,0,,Não é uma rachadura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.61,Denden,,0,0,0,,Está rachado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este é o terceiro andar do\N Pastel Baum de Feijões Vermelhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:49.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O chão começou a\N inclinar demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.41,Denden,,0,0,0,,Não é um terremoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:55.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ouvi uma grande explosão\N há pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um ataque inimigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Continua inclinando!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:03.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,N-Não pode ser...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:07.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está caindo-bon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Whole Cake Château!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:14.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está caindo-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cocoricó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:21.25,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(534,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}A CAPITAL - SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi um tiro inimigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o quartel-general de uma Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:31.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nenhum inimigo pode \Nse infiltrar nesta ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, foi uma explosão?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que explodiu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não deixe cair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos todos morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:45.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso tem a ver com \No casamento no telhado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não brinquem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas estas são ótimas notícias!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acho que sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi no mesmo instante!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que mais poderia ter explodido?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas por que a Caixa Tamate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gente, segurem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E os Chapéus de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não faço ideia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas nos salvou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:45.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estávamos quase morrendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está rolando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:10.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos salvos...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:12.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Embora ainda não saibamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:16.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...se estamos salvos ou não!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:18.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos encrencados, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:25.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Whole Cake Château está desmoronando devido a uma explosão de origem desconhecida!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:40.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:43.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No corpo de Bege não se sente nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:49.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:50.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:53.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...há muito pânico no salão.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:01.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...todo o Whole Cake \NChâteau está tremendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que tipo de brincadeira é essa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou sonhando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:10.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Olha, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:14.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é um desastre!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:18.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem e como fez isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:25.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmãos...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:28.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmãs...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmãos! {pace line:"Oh, my family!" kind of different}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:35.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não consigo parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:36.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:52.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:09.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é magnífico!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.48,0:24:14.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sei quem fez isso,\N mas agradeço!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não precisávamos matá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:19.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com isso,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:22.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,os Piratas da Big Mom, a Yonkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:25.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,estão aniquilados!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:34.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.47,0:24:45.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O castelo é maior que a cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:47.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há escapatória!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:50.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que corramos, não nos salvaremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.28,0:25:02.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.62,0:25:06.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Calma.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.46,0:25:11.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Grandes notícias!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.72,0:25:14.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estas são grandes notícias!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.82,0:25:16.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não está preocupado com sua vida?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.84,0:25:17.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.81,0:25:19.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não consigo voar!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.82,0:25:26.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.27,0:25:32.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...se este fosse o fim dos\N Piratas da Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.52,0:25:34.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,seriam grandes notícias.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.28,0:25:45.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.24,0:25:47.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.74,0:25:49.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.90,0:25:51.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depressa, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.77,0:25:52.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:53.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.83,0:25:57.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estão vivos, hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.16,0:26:00.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpem a espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.42,0:26:01.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que loucura vocês fizeram!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.80,0:26:03.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Caramba!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.74,0:26:06.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Menos mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.10,0:26:07.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vai, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.57,0:26:08.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fuja para longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.90,0:26:11.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nem precisa me dizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.10,0:26:13.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fugir, fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.80,0:26:16.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foram embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.06,0:26:19.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Missão cumprida!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.64,0:26:20.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Retirada!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.94,0:26:22.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.58,0:26:37.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fofo e macio...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.00,0:26:40.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Úmido e macio...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.34,0:26:42.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso na vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.44,0:26:44.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...é impossível de ter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.16,0:26:55.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.98,0:27:00.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:02.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o nosso fim!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.27,0:27:08.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Veränderung Gourmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.27,0:27:08.98,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,5470,5970)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:27:03.27,0:27:08.98,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,5470,5970)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:27:03.27,0:27:08.98,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,5470,5970)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:27:03.27,0:27:08.98,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,5470,5970)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:27:03.27,0:27:08.98,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,5470,5970)}Transformação gourmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.49,0:27:36.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.15,0:27:53.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.46,0:27:55.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.94,0:28:01.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.77,0:28:13.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Creme chantilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.31,0:28:15.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vai nos arrastar!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:21.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é...?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.72,0:28:22.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo fofo?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.50,0:28:39.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.82,0:28:46.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Whole Cake Château se \Ntransformou em um bolo de verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.32,0:28:47.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso nos salvou.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.85,0:28:50.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deve ter sido o grande chefe de cozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.82,0:28:53.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Achei que ia morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.39,0:28:59.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.68,0:29:01.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:04.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu castelo se transformou em bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.19,0:29:11.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os doces criados com \Na habilidade de Streusen...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.94,0:29:15.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...enchem o estômago, \Nmas não têm um bom sabor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.20,0:29:15.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.87,0:29:20.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bom que você está bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.28,0:29:23.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.98,0:29:28.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu bolo de casamento...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:31.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.89,0:29:35.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.53,0:29:36.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me ajudem!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.81,0:29:37.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.89,0:29:39.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já passou tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.69,0:29:41.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Achei que ia morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.44,0:29:43.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bolo vai me esmagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.70,0:29:46.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem uma voz vindo de lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.52,0:29:48.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rápido, vamos ajudá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.35,0:29:51.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Esse é...!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.90,0:29:53.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mont-d'Or-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.56,0:29:55.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que diabos aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.54,0:29:58.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Achei que a cidade seria esmagada\N e que todos morreríamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.84,0:30:00.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Calem a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.29,0:30:01.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.29,0:30:01.02,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.02,0:30:03.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso ainda não acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.48,0:30:07.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqueles que conspiraram para\N matar mama fugiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.49,0:30:10.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles não devem ter ido longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.82,0:30:14.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Contatem todas\N as ilhas de Totto Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.78,0:30:19.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não deixem escapar nem um...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.12,0:30:23.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...dos Piratas do Chapéu de Palha\N nem dos Piratas Firetank!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.66,0:30:30.04,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(537,493)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}NOROESTE DA WHOLE CAKE ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.15,0:30:31.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aqui está seguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:32.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:42.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.57,0:30:44.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente achei que íamos morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.66,0:30:46.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me agradeçam!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.16,0:30:49.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fico enjoado só de pensar \Nque fiz algo bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.81,0:30:52.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu os carreguei!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.18,0:30:53.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desgraçados!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.53,0:30:55.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca, escória!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.32,0:30:59.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lembra do que fez com\N as crianças de Punk Hazard?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.70,0:31:01.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não precisamos mais de você,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.96,0:31:03.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,então pode morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.84,0:31:06.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.05,0:31:08.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como você fala assim com um gênio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.81,0:31:13.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês sabem que eu posso encher tudo\N de gás venenoso, sabem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:16.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Toma.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.32,0:31:17.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seu coração.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.51,0:31:24.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,M-Meu...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.82,0:31:32.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está livre.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.79,0:31:34.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deveria tê-lo esmagado.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.44,0:31:36.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.08,0:31:40.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.82,0:31:43.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deveria tê-lo esmagado.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.18,0:31:55.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu coração...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.18,0:31:59.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu coração voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.86,0:32:02.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nunca mais vou vê-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.18,0:32:06.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Adeus, idiotas e mulher estúpida!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.27,0:32:07.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que ele caiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.54,0:32:09.84,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.72,0:32:09.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, foi repentino.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.84,0:32:10.64,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.84,0:32:12.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que diabos aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.65,0:32:12.21,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Adeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.21,0:32:13.64,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.21,0:32:13.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não consigo imaginar o que\N pode ter acontecido.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.64,0:32:15.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.82,0:32:17.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.98,0:32:23.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No final das contas, Big Mom e toda \Nsua família sobreviveram-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.82,0:32:28.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O castelo desmoronado \Nvirou um bolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.61,0:32:32.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essa é a habilidade de Streusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.08,0:32:38.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sempre foi um mistério.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.92,0:32:43.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não acho que ele seja apenas um chefe de cozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.68,0:32:46.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele deve ser forte em combate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.72,0:32:52.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Achei que seria o fim dos\N Piratas da Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.44,0:32:55.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que azar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.65,0:32:56.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tanto faz.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.98,0:32:58.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O castelo foi destruído.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.82,0:33:00.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me sinto aliviado.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.57,0:33:03.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Adeus, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.41,0:33:05.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora só falta escapar, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.81,0:33:07.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o que estamos fazendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.34,0:33:10.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Houve muitos obstáculos no começo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.32,0:33:11.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.37,0:33:12.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, vamos fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.75,0:33:15.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqui nos separamos, Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.93,0:33:16.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.44,0:33:17.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.59,0:33:20.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Falhamos em assassinar a Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.42,0:33:24.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há justificativa para continuarmos juntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.10,0:33:25.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.88,0:33:28.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É melhor que se apressem.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.28,0:33:33.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo chegando ao seu navio, levará um dia\N para sair do território da Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.36,0:33:34.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.52,0:33:37.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.52,0:33:41.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Castle Tank!
