Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.87,0:33:50.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Os Chapéu de Palha\N foram para lá"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.58,0:33:52.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Não façam besteira!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.96,0:33:54.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.01,0:33:55.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É para sobreviver!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.46,0:33:56.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.77,0:33:59.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe-nos nos despedir-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.57,0:34:02.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu me tornei amiga da Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.05,0:34:03.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não estamos aqui para fazer amigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.42,0:34:07.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora começa a verdadeira fuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.32,0:34:11.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, nós iremos \Npelo Shark Submerge...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.05,0:34:14.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e direto para o Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.09,0:34:15.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.01,0:34:16.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tenham cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.55,0:34:19.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nós também vamos nos apressar \Npara chegar à costa onde atracamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.16,0:34:24.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Forme dois esquadrões, Daifuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.11,0:34:25.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.24,0:34:29.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos dividir em dois\N grupos e persegui-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.75,0:34:32.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um esquadrão irá atrás do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.26,0:34:35.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O outro irá atrás da cabeça de Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.66,0:34:42.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.39,0:34:47.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.24,0:34:49.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ninguém vai escapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:51.27,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.53,0:34:57.03,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Seus ingredientes foram \Nselecionados cuidadosamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.03,0:35:01.37,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O melhor bolo de casamento...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.37,0:35:07.00,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Eu estava com tanta vontade de comê-lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.96,0:35:16.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo de casamento...!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.06,0:35:19.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.94,0:35:29.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está meu bolo de casamento?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.90,0:35:32.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora não...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.48,0:35:35.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Traga-o para mim, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.27,0:35:37.27,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTempos:\NHalee,\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL {i was thinking to add shichibukai fansub to the graphics credits also, since they also do a lot of those}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:42.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:49.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.44,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:05.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:12.34,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:19.93,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e ondeie-as...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:26.81,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:29.77,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:33.15,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.45,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para qual futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:39.95,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.96,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.58,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.13,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.43,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.47,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:09.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos isso há muito tempo.
